{
  "stem": "17426.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 203.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I reported to Dr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Neumann, and Neumann put me aside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He put me in charge of the first group of 400 to go to this [GERMAN] to lead the Kolonie, so-called Kolonie, which is a group in German.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And so I did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But when we came to the work place, they assigned each one to a different foreman.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I was assigned to the kitchen to bring water from a well, with another man.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And that's what our work was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Shortly thereafter, I was chosen to work in the office for the [GERMAN], which was the overseer over the-- the foreman, the head foreman.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I kept hours for the people that came to work because they paid for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[GERMAN] paid to the camp for our work on an hourly basis, which I didn't know but found out a little later.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I had to enter the hours when we came and how many we came each day and when we left, and summarized this, and multiply it, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And also do some work for the technician who was doing field-- field organizing at the time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So this was my work there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "This was lucky.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Into the woods, just about a mile and a half away from the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a field kitchen, sort of like an army kitchen and open space, with two cauldrons where we were giving-- the kitchen-- was for us for soup.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was another kitchen inside the barracks that was for the foremen, food for the foremen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so this man from Kowal by the name of Marek and I were lugging water from there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And on one of our trips, we suddenly heard [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] young female voices singing.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
